              <li><a href="/about#values" class="block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm text-center text-diner-dark border border-diner-border bg-white hover:bg-diner-warm hover:text-diner-red transition-colors">What We Stand For</a></li>
              <li><a href="/contact" class="block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm text-center text-diner-dark border border-diner-border bg-white hover:bg-diner-warm hover:text-diner-red transition-colors">Contact Us</a></li>
